title: Delfonics Wood Ballpoint Pen—White
description:
Founded in 1987, Delfonics is one of the most important modern stationery companies in Japan. Set out with the goal to create "stationery that frees your creativity" and the philosophy that stationery is not only a tool but "an entrance to culture".
  • Dimensions: 6" standard length Size: .07mm tip
  • Materials: Natural wood, black ink.
